    "content": "<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>\n<img width=\"625\" height=\"416\" src=\"http://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/healthcare-625x416.png\" class=\"attachment-medium wp-post-image\" alt=\"healthcare\"></p>\n<p>So the Obama campaign <a onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/barackobama.tumblr.com/post/20060941064/another-reason-to-like-obamacare');\" href=\"http://barackobama.tumblr.com/post/20060941064/another-reason-to-like-obamacare\">posted this</a> yesterday. Discuss.</p>\n<div class=\"clear-line\"></div>\n</div>"
