    "content": "<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>\n<a href=\"http://www.vulture.com/2012/08/meryl-streep-matrix.html\">\n<img width=\"625\" height=\"625\" src=\"http://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Meryl-Streep-scatterplot-625x625.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium wp-post-image\" alt=\"Meryl Streep scatterplot\"></a>\n</p>\n<p>Vulture <a onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/www.vulture.com/2012/08/meryl-streep-matrix.html');\" href=\"http://www.vulture.com/2012/08/meryl-streep-matrix.html\">plotted Meryl Streep's character faces</a> on a cold-warm, frivolous-serious scatterplot. Sure, why not.</p>\n<div class=\"clear-line\"></div>\n</div>"
