    "content": "<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>USA Today launched a redesigned logo last month. It's a circle that reflects the day's news in each section. Stephen Colbert reports.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"http://media.mtvnservices.com/embed/mgid:cms:video:colbertnation.com:419185\" width=\"625\" height=\"351\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>[via @<a onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/twitter.com/albertocairo');\" href=\"http://twitter.com/albertocairo\">albertocairo</a>]</p>\n<div class=\"clear-line\"></div>\n</div>"
